text: Liza Rebecca Weil (born June 5, 1977) is an American actress. She is known for her roles as Paris Geller in the WB/CW comedy-drama series Gilmore Girls and as attorney Bonnie Winterbottom in the ABC legal drama series How to Get Away with Murder. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American child actors Category:American stage actors Category:American voice actors Category:Actors from New Jersey Category:Actors from Pennsylvania Category:People from Passaic, New Jersey
